Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.78,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.41,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,106)\fs17\an7\fnVerdana\c&HF8F6F6&\3c&H2E2D2B&\b0\pos(133.5,119)}Lock\N\N\NSleep\N\N\NShutdown\N\N\NReboot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.02,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,明天见。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.79,DefaultItalics,PA,0,0,0,,感谢您的耐心等待。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:12.09,DefaultItalics,PA,0,0,0,,开往岛田的末班车从2号站台发车。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.36,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊。
