Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.20,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(315,1)\fs22\fnVerdana\c&H1F2029&\3c&HF0F0F0&\bord2\b0\pos(320,138)}June 21
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.34,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:58.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,靠抽完了。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:01.22,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs14\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H7A7B75&\3c&HC1C1BA&\move(422,67,422,101,17,2728)}Genki Trading
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.92,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,今天要做订单表。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.28,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,去打个招呼给新供应商然后……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.60,Default,WEMPLOYEE,0,0,0,,打扰了佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:13.17,Default,WEMPLOYEE,0,0,0,,我家有人突然倒下住院了……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.97,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦没事快去吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.43,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,有急活我来处理。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.80,Default,WEMPLOYEE,0,0,0,,太谢谢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.48,Default,WEMPLOYEE,0,0,0,,喂？好我马上到。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.74,Default,WEMPLOYEE,0,0,0,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.64,Default,WEMPLOYEE,0,0,0,,就这些对不起交给你了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:36.25,Default,MID,0,0,0,,对不起佐佐木先生\N伊藤君今天也不在。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.39,Default,MID,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.13,Default,MID,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生？！
