Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.92,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,我回来了大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:46.07,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,带了特产记得给客户分。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.61,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.03,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,别告诉我你因为下雨就偷懒！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:03.80,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,终于结束了……\N十四天连班地狱。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:07.00,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,总算撑过来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.47,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我们上辈子造了什么孽。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.36,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这该死的雨还下个不停。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.87,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哦你在这儿。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.87,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.12,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好久不见田山小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:36.12,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你没精神吗？有点事想麻烦你。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.66,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好啊如果帮得上忙。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.51,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嘿晴天娃娃。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.97,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好怀念。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:53.04,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,店长每年梅雨季都会挂。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:57.96,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,让来店的小朋友画脸\N员工也画几个。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.02,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:02.52,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,被要求交一份但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.08,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我懂了我画得很烂对吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.03,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,没有……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.80,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你好好看看再说一遍。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:15.29,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,艺术是个性艺术是表达。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.54,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,就是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.83,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,帮我画几张吧佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.60,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,画画啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.37,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不擅长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.18,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这个……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:33.70,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,开会时会涂鸦提神。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.43,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但不知道算不算画。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:40.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.94,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs28\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H212323&\3c&HE4E4E4&\frz25.77\pos(63.5,36)}Gotooooooou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.70,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,为什么是店长？而且好像。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.20,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哈哈哈太好笑了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.44,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我画了你店长。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.26,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,接下来画你。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.00,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,嘿挺可爱的。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.09,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,画你特别好画。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.50,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,一定是因为你总看着我。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.73,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,那我也画你。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.74,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哇画得真好。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.48,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,什么这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.12,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,烟啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:42.15,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我还挺喜欢下雨天的。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:44.44,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,烟更明显。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:48.10,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,味道也比平时好。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.11,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但最近太忙了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:54.12,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,完全忘了这些。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.46,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,是因为在这里抽烟我才……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.90,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.52,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,嗯。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.12,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,晚安佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.13,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs10\b0\pos(284.5,173)\frz11.21}Alarm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.13,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs9\b0\frz11.21\3c&H3443AD&\pos(292,204.5)}Snooze
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.13,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs8\b0\frz11.21\3c&H676767&\pos(298,242)}Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.55,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,该死。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.34,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,忘了关闹钟。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.40,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,太累了在田山小姐旁边睡着了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.15,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,得休息一整天……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:45.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.90,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(352,1)\fs20\fnComic Sans MS\c&H292A30&\frz340.9\pos(281,277.5)}Proud of ya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.50,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.03,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等、等等这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.34,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:10:00.23,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐这是油性笔……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:03.04,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(435,1)\fs22\fnVerdana\c&H1F2029&\3c&HF0F0F0&\bord2\b0\pos(320,127)}July 5\N\N\N\N\N\NFirst day off in 15
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.08,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs16\fnComic Sans MS\c&H353532&\frz340.9\pos(287.5,253)}Proud of ya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:45.08,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs16\bord2\c&HC9E6F9&\3c&H6F80DF&\frz11.31\fax-0.2\pos(133,125.5)}24-Hour
