Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:54.09,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs16\bord2\fnGeorgia\c&H3626D5&\3c&HF8FAF5&}Well-done Pork Bone Broth\N{\fs30}Extra-Large {\fs18}Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:15.95,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,开饭了——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:20.12,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你不是说要少吃拉面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:24.12,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,没事吃了我能消耗掉。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.54,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:29.46,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,在你干劲十足的时候说不好意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.24,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你今天早退。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:36.26,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,啊？不能在我吃饭前说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.92,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,怪我咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.90,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,今天客少不想浪费人工费。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:45.14,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你的班最好调。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:51.38,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,还是留下帮忙查冷冻食品保质期？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.03,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好吧我走。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:03.28,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,早点说的话回家路上还能去吃碗拉面.。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.39,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,懒得化妆了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.79,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,买点酒后面抽根烟回家睡觉。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.23,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,真不巧佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.10,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,山田小姐今晚不在哦。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.80,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,说曹操曹操到。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.25,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,他今天正常下班了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:24.34,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,正好从后面吓他一跳。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:25.26,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.68,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:30.45,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不过已经老套路了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.69,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.39,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,晚上好。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.95,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生你的篮子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不好意思晚上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.29,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.95,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs18\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H093BDB&\3c&H000751&\pos(221,215)}Satisfaction 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:52.70,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,没没事走神不小心掉了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.04,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,她穿私服？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.09,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,能看到山田小姐穿便服我可以治愈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.04,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不行不准盯着看。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.57,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,自然点谁都有私服。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.20,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,连我都穿！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.35,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.36,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你在这儿。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.88,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,非常感谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:23.53,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H343434&\3c&HF3F4F2&\move(416,52,-450,52)\clip(m 0 0 l 410 3 433 37 414 54 404 74 410 82 411 88 411 97 413 104 417 117 426 134 434 145 0 157)}Jugemu Jugemu Goko-no-Surikire Kaijari-Suigyo No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:23.79,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,寿限无寿限无扔屎机……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:26.08,DefaultTop,YAMADA,0,0,0,,在看零食？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.12,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯配酒吃。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.98,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,那我也买点。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.63,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,嘿这个饼干很好吃。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.70,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.51,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,哦有新口味。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:44.39,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,但买了甜的又想吃咸的。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.89,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,嗯……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:47.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,山田小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你看到这三根烟了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,能各配一个零食吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.26,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好的……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:01.90,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.74,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.16,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,就是这个。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:11.04,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,弹出来那根对应的就是你想吃的。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:17.31,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦对不起不该替你决定。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.54,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我买！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.53,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你经常用这个方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.05,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.46,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,算是我的小迷信。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:35.11,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,第一根弹出来今天能早回家。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.81,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,第二根弹出来这周能休息一天。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.64,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,第三根弹出来今天收银台……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.39,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,算了。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.71,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你能决定零食就好。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.03,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那我走了。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.22,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,路上小心。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.75,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好佐佐木先生也是。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.26,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,「第三根弹出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.86,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,今天山田小姐在收银台」。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.84,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,就算你打住也明显得很。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.73,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,努力保持绅士风度的先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.34,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,第三根弹出来他就会发现。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.74,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,第二根他就不会。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.46,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,如果第一根……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:47.93,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,感觉佐佐木先生要倒霉。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.24,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.52,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,被山田小姐的便服弄晕了。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.42,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,忘了胳膊下还夹着这本杂志！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:03.77,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,没付钱就带出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.52,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\t(25,2736,\fscx111.74\fscy111.74)\bord2\fs12\c&H717879&\3c&HD1D8D9&\frz9.82\fax-0.2\move(299,58,301.3,45.28,25,2736)}Office
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.53,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:09.19,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,我们非常重视偷窃行为。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.67,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起我不是故意的。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.66,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,每个人都这么说佐佐木君。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:20.20,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,305)\fs16\bord2\c&HF9EBFD&\3c&H5C2BB7&\frz11.31\fax-0.2\move(135,151,135,300,22,5070)}24-Hour
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:20.20,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,305)\fnArial Black\bord2\c&H724DB8&\3c&HEFE4E4&\fax-0.15\frz9.24\4c&H997A5F&\shad2\move(286,177.5,286,326.5,22,5070)}Supermarket S
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.21,0:16:21.43,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉！
